N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4810.8 - Limit on identification numbers and licenses issued

State Regulations

When an organization has more than two affiliates or
auxiliaries, no identification number or license shall be issued to more than
three such organizations. Notes
